# Narrativo - Development Plan

## File Structure

``` markdown
src/    
├── components/    
│   ├── Navbar.astro       # Navigation bar component    
│   ├── Footer.astro       # Footer component    
│   ├── StoryCard.astro    # Reusable card component for stories    
│   ├── BlogCard.astro     # Reusable card component for blogs    
│   └── ContactForm.astro  # Contact form component    
│
├── layouts/
│   ├── MainLayout.astro   # Main layout wrapper for pages    
│   └── StoryLayout.astro  # Layout specific to single story pages    
│
├── pages/
│   ├── index.astro        # Homepage    
│   ├── about.astro        # About page    
│   ├── contact.astro      # Contact page    
│   ├── privacy-policy.astro # Privacy policy page    
│   ├── terms.astro        # Terms of service page    
│   │
│   ├── blog/    
│   │   ├── index.astro    # Blog listing page    
│   │   └── [slug].astro   # Individual blog post pages    
│   │    
│   ├── stories/    
│   │   ├── index.astro    # Stories listing page    
│   │   └── [slug].astro   # Individual story pages    
│   │    
│   └── dashboard/    
│       └── index.astro    # User dashboard page    
│    
├── styles/    
│   ├── globals.css        # Global styles with Tailwind imports    
│   └── custom.css         # Custom reusable styles (if needed)    
│    
└── utils/    
    └── helpers.js         # Utility functions (e.g., format dates)
```    